<h2 style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333; text-align: center;">Ticket Notification</h2>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Dear <%= engineer_name %>,</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">A new ticket has been assigned to you and requires your immediate attention.</p>
<p style="font-size: 26px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;">Ticket Details:</p>
<ul style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #333333; padding-left: 20px;">
    <li><strong>Ticket ID:</strong>"<%= newTicket_id %>"</li>
    <li><strong>Customer Name:</strong>"<%= customer_name %>"</li>
    <li><strong>Issue Description:</strong>"<%= issue_description %>"</li>
    <li><strong>Priority:</strong>"<%= priority %>"</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">You can view the full request details below:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
    <a href="<%= baseUrl %>/tickets/<%= newTicket_id %>" 
        style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: #0056b3; border-radius: 5px;">
        View Ticket Details
    </a>
</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Please address this ticket as soon as possible</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Best regards, <br>
    The support team
</p>
